# 强制所有文本文件以 LF 入库与检出，消除 Windows/CI 行尾差异。
# 之前 core.autocrlf=true 导致本地 CRLF / 仓库 LF 混杂，CI 上 prettier
# format:check 与本地结果不一致。.gitattributes 优先级高于 autocrlf。
* text=auto eol=lf

# 二进制文件不做行尾转换
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.icns binary
*.node binary
*.zip binary
*.7z binary
*.gz binary
*.exe binary
*.dll binary
*.lib binary
*.so binary
*.dylib binary
*.wasm binary
